Description: Univention helper programs for debian/rules
 A collection of programs that can be used in a debian/rules file to
 automate common tasks related to building UCS packages. Programs
 are included to install various files into your package. Most Univention
 packages use debhelper as part of their build process.
 .
 This package is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS),
 an integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: https://www.univention.de/
